Package: RBiblioSynth
Type: Package
Title: Bibliometric Analysis and Systematic Review Report Automation
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2026-03-25
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "RBiblioSynth",
      family = "Maintainers",
      email = "opensource@rbibliosynth.org",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Author: RBiblioSynth Maintainers [aut, cre]
Maintainer: RBiblioSynth Maintainers <opensource@rbibliosynth.org>
Description: A modular framework for automating bibliometric analysis and
    systematic review reporting. Provides module M0 for data orchestration
    (load, merge, organize sources from Scopus, WoS, OpenAlex), M1 for main
    information extraction, M2 for annual production regression, M3 for
    country-level analysis, with PRISMA 2020 flow diagram generation.
